payment_confirmed.message:
Hey {username}! 🎉

Your payment has been confirmed and your NIP-05 identity is now active!

✅ Username: {username}@{domain}
💰 Amount: {amount_sats} sats
⏰ Expires: {expires_at}

You can now use your NIP-05 identifier across all Nostr clients. Welcome to the decentralized future!

🔗 Verify your identity: https://{domain}/.well-known/nostr.json?name={username}

